						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up in front of the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>Kākatīya Pratāparudra.</p>						

						<p>Dated <hi rend="italic">Rudhirōdgāri, Vishu-sankrānti.</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers gifts of land altogether ten <hi rend="italic">puṭṭis</hi> in areas in three villages as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> by Nāgadēvarāja as <hi rend="italic">bhōgavṛitti</hi> to god Svayaṁbhūdēva of Darśi for the merit of the king as well as of Jaṟudēva, the donor's father. (See. <hi rend="italic">N.D.I.</hi> Part I, p. 29, Darśi 10).</p>						

						</summary>
